{
  "texts": [
    "An effective strategy involves the design of a BSIC that can be shared among stakeholders.",
    "This BSIC would assign a distinct identifier to each DT simulation model (Angjeliu, Coronelli, and Cardani 2020).",
    "It would also encompass pertinent information pertaining to DT objectives, ownership, and data access authorizations.",
    "Through creating a BSIC, various stakeholders can readily recognize and establish lines of communication with one another.",
    "They can also seamlessly exchange data and foster efficient collaboration."
  ]
}